{"word":"H5608 - סָפַר - çâphar - saw-far' - Commune","slug":"H5608","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">סָפַר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>çâphar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>saw-far'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Commune"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E1;&#x05E4;&#x05E8; - sa&#x0302;phar</b> - <i>saw-far'</i><p/>A primitive root; properly to <i>score</i> with a mark as a tally or record, that is, (by implication) to <i>inscribe</i>, and also to <i>enumerate</i>; intensively to <i>recount</i>, that is, <i>celebrate: - </i>commune, (ac-) count, declare, number, + penknife, reckon, scribe, shew forth, speak, talk, tell (out), writer."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4557\">H4557</a>, <a href=\"#/H4558\">H4558</a>, <a href=\"#/H4559\">H4559</a>, <a href=\"#/H5610\">H5610</a>, <a href=\"#/H5611\">H5611</a>, <a href=\"#/H5612\">H5612</a>, <a href=\"#/H5614\">H5614</a>, <a href=\"#/H5615\">H5615</a>, <a href=\"#/H5616\">H5616</a>, <a href=\"#/H5617\">H5617</a>, <a href=\"#/H5618\">H5618</a>"}]}